      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on that bit about the people on the corner? I want to get more specific with the characters to really heighten the danger. Like, what kind of people are hanging out there that would make someone feel truly unsafe? Give me some more detail on their appearance and what they're doing to make the vibe feel so heavy and threatening.",
